Blanche of Navarre (1137-1156). Queen Consort, wife of Sancho III, king of Castile. Death of the Queen giving birth to her son, the future King Alfonso VIII of Castile. Relief. Sepulcher of Queen Blanche. Romanesque style. 12th century. Monasterio de Santa Mari?a la Real. Najera. La Rioja. Spain.
